Harrison Barnes ‚Äì aka 'The Senator' ‚Äì has expressed an interest in running for senate once his playing career is over.  So while that may be years away, it hasn't stopped him from creating this new animated "How To Vote" civics tutorial similar to the popular throwback political shorts of the 90's. 

In a conversation with an animated Ballot, Harrison explains popular votes, electoral votes and the tricky nuances of it all.  This video is Harrison's approach to encouraging people to make their voices heard in the presidential election and to "not let harsh rhetoric divide us." 

"Your vote is your voice, don't miss the opportunity to be heard," said Barnes.

Credit: Red Bull Media House
